MatchedRegions.transcript: In each experiment, all the instances from a specific family form the test set, while those instances belong to other families are used for training.

MatchedRegion.Text: 2. In each experiment, all the instances from a specific family form the test set while those instances belong to other families are used for training.

MatchedRegions.transcript: And we can find that the model generalizes well on animal species, where there are similarities between training and test species.

MatchedRegion.Text: 1. The model generalizes well on animal species where there are similarities between the training and test species;

MatchedRegions.transcript: And for others, the model doesn't generalize well.

MatchedRegion.Text: 2. For animal species that do not have such similarities, the model does not generalize well.
